22:18.247 --> 22:20.582
Could be part
of the games, maybe.

22:22.251 --> 22:24.954
Very funny, Giannis.

22:25.087 --> 22:27.655
Fortunately, I don't think
you've got the wherewithal

22:27.790 --> 22:30.026
to make a workable
fucking cross!

22:31.626 --> 22:34.163
What's wrong, Lily?
